VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)-ExecutionPolicy\s+(?:Bypass|Unrestricted)|Set-ExecutionPolicy\s+(?:Bypass|Unrestricted)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:-ExecutionPolicy\s+Bypass|Set-ExecutionPolicy\s+Bypass|executionpolicy.*bypass && MISSING:test|CI|pipeline|development|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects PowerShell execution policy bypass or unrestricted policy settings.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Bypass Execution Policy.
